com.badlogic.gdx.graphics.models
Class MD2Mesh

java.lang.Object
  com.badlogic.gdx.graphics.models.MD2Mesh

public final class MD2Mesh
extends java.lang.Object

Encapsulates a loaded MD2Mesh. Not to useful on its own so combine it with one or more MD2Instances. Can be loaded via the MD2Loader class. The MD2Mesh has to be disposed via MD2Mesh.dispose() when it is no longer used.

Author:
mzechner
